## 상품 API
### 상풍 목록 조회
GET {{baseUrl}}/products
Content-Type: application/json

### 상품 조회
GET {{baseUrl}}/products/1
Content-Type: application/json

### 상품 추가
POST {{baseUrl}}/products
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "부리또",
  "price": 30000,
  "imageUrl": "http://example.com/burrito.jpg"
}

### 상품 수정
PUT {{baseUrl}}/products/4
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "부리또",
  "price": 10000,
  "imageUrl": "http://example.com/burrito.jpg"
}

### 상품 삭제
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/products/4

